{"word":"παράκλησις","slug":"παράκλησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παράϰλησις, εως, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρακαλέω\">παρακαλέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘emboldening for facing or carrying out a responsibility or task’, <b>exhortation, encouragement <a href='B:510 13:15'>Ac 13:15</a>; <a href='B:510 15:31'>15:31</a>; <a href='B:520 12:8'>Ro 12:8</a>; <a href='B:520 15:4'>15:4f</a>; <a href='B:530 14:3'>1 Cor 14:3</a>; <a href='B:540 8:4'>2 Cor 8:4</a>, <a href='B:540 8:17'>17</a>; <a href='B:570 2:1'>Phil 2:1</a>; <a href='B:590 2:3'>1 Th 2:3</a>; <a href='B:610 4:13'>1 Ti 4:13</a>; <a href='B:650 6:18'>Hb 6:18</a>; <a href='B:650 12:5'>12:5</a>; <a href='B:650 13:22'>13:22</a>.</b> <el>υἱὸς π.</el> <b><a href='B:510 4:36'>Ac 4:36</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘heartening in time of trouble’, through word or demeanor’, <b>consolation, comfort <a href='B:490 2:25'>Lk 2:25</a>; <a href='B:490 6:24'>6:24</a>; <a href='B:510 9:31'>Ac 9:31</a>; <a href='B:540 1:3-7'>2 Cor 1:3-7</a>; <a href='B:540 7:4'>7:4</a>, <a href='B:540 7:7'>7</a>, <a href='B:540 7:13'>13</a>; <a href='B:600 2:16'>2 Th 2:16</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 7</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρακέκλημαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παράκλητος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}